TreeIter - Class in tsp
 
TreeIter(Collection<Integer>, int, Graph) - Constructor for class tsp.TreeIter
Create an iterator to traverse the set of vertices in unvisited which are successors of currentVertex in g Vertices are stored in a TreeSet sorting by cost and a HashMap is used to translate the cost to the index of each vertex The iterator returns the index of the lowest cost vertex first

TSP1 - Class in tsp
